{"lemma":"أُفُقِ","slug":"أُفُقِ","root":"#.ف.ق","root_slug":"_-ف-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ف-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أُفُق","root":"أفق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n937","n939","n940","n941","n942"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8F%D9%81%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَفَقَ (ʔafaqa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"horizon"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"field of vision"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"climate, region, country, realm (esp. outlying regions)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"distant land"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the wide world","tags":["in-plural"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to attain, to reach","tags":["archaic"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to surpass, to outrange","tags":["archaic"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ء ف ق (ʔ f q), meaning \"to reach the limit\".\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":["/ʔu.fuq/","/ʔa.fa.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n937","headword_ar":"اَفَقَ","root":"Afq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoqN","text_ar":"اَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went his own way, at random,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heedlessly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiba raA^osahu","text_ar":"رَكِبَ رَاْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and went away in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=faAq","text_ar":"ا=فَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the land"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Lth, JK, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he went away in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into, the land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"country:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took his way into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=fAq","text_ar":"ا=فاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqa","text_ar":"اَفَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above; thus, says IB, accord. to Kz, and thus it is given on the authority of Kr; (TA;) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=fiqN","text_ar":"ا=فِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afiqa","text_ar":"اَفِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqN","text_ar":"اَفَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained the utmost degree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though he reached the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufuq","text_ar":"اُفُق"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or horizon, or furthest point of view,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in generosity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"science;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in chasteness of speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquence, and in the combination of excellent qualities."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  Also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqa","text_ar":"اَفَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kr, Ibn-'Abbád, JK, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoqN","text_ar":"اَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He overcame,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surpassed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, Ibn-'Abbád, JK, K.) ―         -b4-  And, inf. n,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufuwqN","text_ar":"اُفُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was goodly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beautiful; he possessed the quality of exciting admiration and approval by his beauty and the pleasingness of his aspect;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a camel, and of a horse. (JK.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqa Ealayohi","text_ar":"اَفَقَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excelled him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, another man: (JK:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he preceded him in excellence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outwent him therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqahu","text_ar":"اَفَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [It is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAqahu","text_ar":"فَاقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqa fiY AlEaTaA='i","text_ar":"اَفَقَ فِى العَطَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoqN","text_ar":"اَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to some more than to others."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) So in the saying of El-Aashà,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"walaA Almalika Aln~uEomaAnu yawoma laqiytuhu\n                      \n                      \n                        bigiboTatihi yuEoTiY AlquTuwTa wa yaA^ofiqu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nor the King En-Noamán, on the day that I met him, in his goodly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"happy, condition, giving gifts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stipends,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"written obligations conferring gifts, and giving to some more than to others"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"writs of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gifts, and sealing"},{"kind":"text","text":"them: or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking his way into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=fAq","text_ar":"ا=فاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqahu","text_ar":"اَفَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afoqN","text_ar":"اَفْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He tanned it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(namely a hide)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until it became what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afiyq","text_ar":"اَفِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, * K.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","K","TK","Lth","O","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n939","headword_ar":"اُفْقٌ","root":"Afq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufuqN","text_ar":"اُفُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n940","headword_ar":"اَفَقٌ","root":"Afq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main and middle part"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanan","text_ar":"سَنَن"},{"kind":"text","text":") of a road; (K;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surface,"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (IAar, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=faAqN","text_ar":"ا=فَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada","text_ar":"قَعَدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN EalaY A^afaqi AlT~ariyqi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ عَلَى اَفَقِ الطَّرِيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one sat upon the main and middle part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surface, of the road"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flanks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ilia:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skins;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aribotu Hat~aY malaA^otu A^afaqiy","text_ar":"شَرِبْتُ حَتَّى مَلَاْتُ اَفَقِي"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I drank until I filled my skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaqapN","text_ar":"اَفَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAar;) which signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flank;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K;) as does also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=fiqapN","text_ar":"ا=فِقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Th, K.) ―         -b3-  Also pl., (S, K,) or [rather] quasi-pl. n., (M, K,) of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afiyqN","text_ar":"اَفِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (S, M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["IAar","K","JK","S","M"]},{"entry_id":"n941","headword_ar":"اَفِقٌ","root":"Afq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afiyqN","text_ar":"اَفِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n942","headword_ar":"اُفُقٌ","root":"Afq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, Mgh, Msb, K, &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufoqN","text_ar":"اُفْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A side;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a lateral,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an outward"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjacent, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a part, region, quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract, considered with respect to its collocation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"juxtaposition"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"direction,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"considered as belonging to a whole;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a remote side;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAHiyapN","text_ar":"نَاحِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, S, Mgh, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a border,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an extremity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK;) of a land, or of the earth; and of the sky, or heavens: (JK, Mgh, Msb:) [or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horizon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part next to the horizon, of the sky"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what appears of the sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~awaAHiY","text_ar":"النَّوَاحِى"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the celestial sphere,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the borders,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremities, of the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place whence blows the south wind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the north wind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the west wind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the east wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=faAqN","text_ar":"ا=فَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK, S, Mgh, Msb, K:) and the sing. also is used as a pl.; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulokN","text_ar":"فُلْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as is said in"},{"kind":"page_break","n":69},{"kind":"text","text":"the Nh: (MF:) thus in the verse of El-'Abbás, in praise of the Prophet:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A^anota lam~a wulidota A^a$oraqati AlA^aro\n                      \n                      \n                        DuwaDaA='a to binuwrika AlA^ufuqu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When thou wast born, the earth became bright, and the tracts of the horizon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the regions, shone with thy light"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAfq","text_ar":"الافق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is made fem. by him as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAHiyapu","text_ar":"النَّاحِيَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) The phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hiyna yagiybu AlA^ufuqu","text_ar":"حِينَ يَغِيبُ الاُفُقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When the redness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness, in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufuq","text_ar":"اُفُق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horizon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disappears."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b2-  Also, in like manner, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lateral part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tent: (JK:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part between the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anterior"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of wood called the"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zir~aAni","text_ar":"زِرَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part called the"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAq","text_ar":"رِوَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":", of a tent: (K:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lateral parts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tent of the kind belonging to the Arabs of the desert. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ufuqN","text_ar":"اُفُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also said to be a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afiyqN","text_ar":"اَفِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is disallowed by Lh. (TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=fiqN","text_ar":"ا=فِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K","JK","Mgh","Msb","TA","MF"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}